{"tid":815393,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日靚午餐 米蘭式煙肉芝士茄茸焗豬柳配飯","createTime":"2018-09-12T04:38:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T04:10:01.000Z","uid":33359,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6874698be2ba09ce2af6ac57ed3e0358987d2c5b","tid":815393,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:38:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/12/123831_b2b0465ec01494eff345386acfb33fda.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F12%2F123831_b2b0465ec01494eff345386acfb33fda.png&h=22fa0f6d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c52fcd6fb48323ec6912edd68751450b5502db7f","tid":815393,"uid":7818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:39:28.000Z","msg":"米蘭頹飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8466ac6b6b68b51c5483578cabec1a7aefd953f","tid":815393,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c52fcd6fb48323ec6912edd68751450b5502db7f","tid":815393,"uid":7818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:39:28.000Z","msg":"米蘭頹飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:40:09.000Z","msg":"米蘭站<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ed5c81a1c2db6ce43a6676d40c93ba73ed0ca5e","tid":815393,"uid":128741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:40:22.000Z","msg":"點解你日日有正野食<br />\n我日日食狗飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94982d5774ccad5bad8ced43e50fb6b2c9c8f45","tid":815393,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"4ed5c81a1c2db6ce43a6676d40c93ba73ed0ca5e","tid":815393,"uid":128741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:40:22.000Z","msg":"點解你日日有正野食<br />\n我日日食狗飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:40:55.000Z","msg":"觀塘返工福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7d61a8a0277cada2fc565f4c23b83fef61e951","tid":815393,"uid":113064,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:42:45.000Z","msg":"一剔過<br />\nA、B、C、D餐係固定午餐<br />\n而E、F、G、H餐係每星期都轉一次<br />\n連埋蒜包餐湯凍飲 原價$45 / 48 / 50蚊<br />\n1230前埋單 / 1415後入坐減5蚊<br />\n盛惠$40 / 43 / 45蚊<br />\n推介菜式係皇牌燒雞 + 避風塘脆薯皇<br />\n星期六會送埋甜品 暫時係焦糖燉蛋<br />\n有緣仲會見到連登飲食台<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>堅硬台柱</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>受薪偏頗</strong></span></span>飲食評論<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>打手部主管</strong></span></span>&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">慘過番印度</span></span><br />\n<br />\n百里香 觀塘駿業街67號熟食市場1樓44號<br />\n路線：港鐵觀塘站A2出口 步行約6分鐘<br />\n營業時間：一至五11:00-16:30；六11:00-16:00<br />\n外賣熱線：<span style=\"color: gold;\">67082851</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">資料由<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">原創者</span>以無邊溫柔Mane提供</span>"},{"pid":"f4a4434537ae928c07bd392ffb7f43eca05b719e","tid":815393,"uid":33359,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:45:59.000Z","msg":"講下味道先<br />\n舊煙肉正到飛起<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係用香煎而唔係鬼佬鐘意個隻油炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n面個層芝士好香濃 上菜前先用焗爐焗一焗 芝士完全融入煙肉到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食落喉嚨好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n豬柳唔算特別嫩滑 一入口先係好濃香草味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後肉香先慢慢滲出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b0326d6a68686caef1924cd7a2c4933d72ed328","tid":815393,"uid":67329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:47:10.000Z","msg":"米蘭式即係點<br />\n邊度米蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91cba90ea6f4d421ead36f5dc3e6457879a02a6b","tid":815393,"uid":33359,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"3b0326d6a68686caef1924cd7a2c4933d72ed328","tid":815393,"uid":67329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:47:10.000Z","msg":"米蘭式即係點<br />\n邊度米蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:49:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/12/124911_5a8e9d9a1d2a2e43aa571c1c535db6ae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F12%2F124911_5a8e9d9a1d2a2e43aa571c1c535db6ae.png&h=c8e89a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFrom百里香fb"},{"pid":"149ae263efdafc46efb8526fdccd5828fd07e9fe","tid":815393,"uid":36876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:55:51.000Z","msg":"剩係叫一個佢送唔送? 成業街個面"},{"pid":"dde9c7d023181699d4502cc1ca4891b39cd1dc41","tid":815393,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"149ae263efdafc46efb8526fdccd5828fd07e9fe","tid":815393,"uid":36876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:55:51.000Z","msg":"剩係叫一個佢送唔送? 成業街個面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T04:58:07.000Z","msg":"你打去問<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係繁忙時間應該送掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2337ba40ef55ebbec564a86eec07ccceed1380c3","tid":815393,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:02:24.000Z","msg":"你叫佢改下汁<br />\n成日都茄汁<br />\n唔係唔好食<br />\n但好悶"},{"pid":"8ddc980b46ab306be5e37c0eab1e7e6c653e3172","tid":815393,"uid":74595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:18:50.000Z","msg":"好想食 營業時間撞返工時間"},{"pid":"0b71a8de5facaeb0b7f3f939c672b47a04c8ea1f","tid":815393,"uid"